src:
MFK hadde tre spillere som tjente mer enn to millioner kroner i fjor. RBK hadde 15.
05 Nov 2019, 11:28 by Martin Brøste
Store lønnsforskjeller mellom erkerivalene.
Molde er i ferd med å cruise inn til et etterlengtet seriegull, og kan sikre eliteserietrofeet dersom de slår Strømsgodset på Aker Stadion søndag.
text:
MFK had three players who earned more than NOK 2 million last year. RBK had 15.
05 Nov 2019, 11:28 by Martin Brøste
Large pay differences between arch rivals.
Molde is about to cruise in for a long-awaited series gold, and can secure the elite series trophy if they beat the Strømsgodset at Aker Stadium on Sunday.
